{"tid":143212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺茶餐廳食老本問題嚴重？","createTime":"2017-03-04T12:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T16:57:27.000Z","uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5880a322e49f49d34bcc54abee03a8f92ff194e","tid":143212,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"屌你咩 間茶餐廳菜單十年都無新菜式<br />\n我對住樓下間茶記食一年已經悶死<br />\n每次叫野食都諗左勁耐先勉強揀來食<br />\n<br />\n成個餐單有八成菜式都有肉、熱氣、高熱量<br />\n<br />\n我唔想食佢D肉，因為次次都勁&ldquo;唉&rdquo;口<br />\n<br />\n我舉例：佢有兩個滑蛋菜式<br />\n1)滑蛋蝦仁飯&mdash;&gt;我唔中意食蝦，膠味濃既蝦更加唔中意<br />\n2)滑蛋牛肉飯&mdash;&gt;上面講左，次次都係老牛，咬唔開<br />\n<br />\n我比較喜歡食清淡D既菜式<br />\n我即刻諗到，點解佢唔試下出：<br />\n1)時菜滑蛋飯&mdash;&gt;雖然佢D時菜永遠都係菜芯，但清淡<br />\n2)魚香茄子菜芯飯<br />\n<br />\n其實每個菜式加返D菜就已經好好多<br />\n<br />\n暫時咁多先，遲D補充，各位巴絲都可以留低你地對茶記既意見"},{"pid":"bec5324be54808f8587cae23c04cf0be6a573f2b","tid":143212,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麥當勞夠年年月月都係雞牛豬薯條汽水"},{"pid":"04d8120ba487612986eb796380c7ac76c5a11d0f","tid":143212,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"追唔上時代<br />\n應該轉賣分子料理"},{"pid":"d98f1d2072a69f51e4cda77210179a1884371866","tid":143212,"uid":50872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"茶餐廳既特色就係食老本"},{"pid":"98372210a7f2b76d1f36c2a3ee84d9a1d9eb6284","tid":143212,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"茶記平返少少我已經好滿足<br />\n坐地起價屌你老母"},{"pid":"2a89c255207cb211e2c2c780fec9d7dcc888f983","tid":143212,"uid":545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"咁創新就唔係茶餐廳啦"},{"pid":"2996a1509627bcc8ff02fa24248b38da7d13009f","tid":143212,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:42:45.000Z","msg":"舉例果啲係個廚煮得差<br />\n你諗果啲好奇怪<br />\n其實可以考慮嗌碟菜"},{"pid":"1dcec97ecfbf347f6ab5c659fee450580c373361","tid":143212,"uid":55272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"最重要係杯奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068b55121488a85179c0f064e5bb6f2614820972","tid":143212,"uid":76227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最重要係杯奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意。杯奶茶難飲，就算啲野有幾好食都減哂分"},{"pid":"3e4144866c81787a68c264cd8eb5d592fb696fa0","tid":143212,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舉例果啲係個廚煮得差<br />\n你諗果啲好奇怪<br />\n其實可以考慮嗌碟菜</blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者去味精粥麵店"},{"pid":"8b74a0a384ece8989e92d789b36898d7e553c4cb","tid":143212,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪唔好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麥當勞夠年年月月都係雞牛豬薯條汽水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我已經無食麥當勞好耐"},{"pid":"6f8fcfc9c32f2fd8e3ef5fa53132d115a1554d46","tid":143212,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶記平返少少我已經好滿足<br />\n坐地起價屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagree 賣垃圾仲要咁貴"},{"pid":"09faabab536c890e24d94ac95b72c608e03ea33f","tid":143212,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁創新就唔係茶餐廳啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解茶餐廳唔可以創新？"},{"pid":"036e9069b8b0f824e2b3d22bfc3908f3b6e139eb","tid":143212,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舉例果啲係個廚煮得差<br />\n你諗果啲好奇怪<br />\n其實可以考慮嗌碟菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨叫菜$70 又係食垃圾<br />\n比起叫飯係平$30"},{"pid":"f1a370562ab6a3d4174aa5f2a1d67c992777f686","tid":143